Metadata: University of California Sea Grant /San Diego County Cooperative Extension

Tidelines will be published quarterly as a local newsletter dealing with practical problems in the areas of Commercial and sport fisheries; Seafood processing, aquaculture, marine education and youth programs, marine research, waterfront management, boating industry, marine transportation, environmental policy, and coastal engineering. Cover articles include: Safety at Sea, Ports to "Stow it!", Props pinch petrol pennies, Energy conservation loan program is big success.
